{"word":"Embroidery","slug":"embroidery","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Embroidery</b> In blue and purple and scarlet:<br/> - On the curtains of the tabernacle<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=26&verse=1'>Exo 26:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=26&verse=36'>Exo 26:36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=27&verse=16'>Exo 27:16</a> <br/> - On the girdle and coat of the high priest, mingled with gold<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=28&verse=4'>Exo 28:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=28&verse=39'>Exo 28:39</a> <br/> On the garments of Sisera<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=5&verse=30'>Jdg 5:30</a><br/> On the garments of princes<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=26&verse=16'>Eze 26:16</a><br/> On the garments of women<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=45&verse=14'>Psa 45:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=16&verse=10'>Eze 16:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=16&verse=13'>Eze 16:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=16&verse=18'>Eze 16:18</a><br/> Bezaleel and Aholiab divinely inspired for, in the work of the tabernacle<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=35&verse=35'>Exo 35:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=38&verse=23'>Exo 38:23</a><br/><a href='S:Tapestry'>Tapestry</a>"}]}